<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="term-n">term <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tɜːm/    美 /tɜːrm/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 学期：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>in the <strong>spring / summer / autumn term</strong>
在春季/夏季/秋季学期</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 时期；期限：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>during one’s <strong>term in office</strong>
在某人任职期间</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 术语：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>scientific / medical terms
科学/医学术语</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-the-long-short-term">in the long / short term</h3>
<p>1.<strong>从长远 / 眼前看</strong>  </p></div>